episodes.title: Lawsuit claims polygamous sect traffics children for sex, labor
episodes.description:
Ten plaintiffs are suing the polygamous Kingston Group and its leaders, alleging they coerce girls into teenage marriages, facilitate sex abuse and steal wages from followers assigned to work at sect-controlled businesses.

FULL STORY - https://www.fox13now.com/news/fox-13-investigates/lawsuit-claims-polygamous-sect-traffics-children-for-sex-labor
